MIAMI Fixtures for the sixth International Champions Cup tournament of pre-season football matches: July 20: Manchester City v Borussia Dortmund (Chicago), Sevilla v Benfica (Zurich) July 22: Liverpool v Borussia Dortmund (Charlotte) July 25: Manchester City v Liverpool (East Rutherford, New Jersey), AC Milan v Manchester United (Pasadena, California), Roma v Tottenham Hotspur (San Diego), Borussia Dortmund v Benfica (Pittsburgh), Juventus v Bayern Munich (Philadelphia) July 26: Arsenal v Atletico Madrid (Singapore) July 28: Bayern Munich v Manchester City (Miami), Manchester United v Liverpool (Ann Arbor, Michigan), Barcelona v Tottenham Hotspur (Pasadena, California), Benfica v Juventus (Harrison, New Jersey), Arsenal v Paris Saint-Germain (Singapore) July 30: Paris Saint-Germain v Atletico Madrid (Singapore) July 31: Manchester United v Real Madrid (Miami), AC Milan v Tottenham Hotspur (Minneapolis, Minnesota), Barcelona v Roma (Arlington, Texas) August 1: Inter Milan v Chelsea (Gothenburg, Sweden) August 4: Real Madrid v Juventus (Landover, Maryland), AC Milan v Barcelona (Santa Clara, California), Arsenal v Chelsea (Stockholm, Sweden) August 7: Real Madrid v Roma (East Rutherford, New Jersey), Sevilla v Inter Milan (Lecce, Italy) August 12: Inter Milan v Atletico Madrid (Madrid, Spain) To Be Determined: Paris Saint-Germain v Bayern Munich (Klagenfurt, Austria), Sevilla v Chelsea (Warsaw, Poland)  